    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "God’s children, we’re born to be kings with His Son,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And we need to be trained that we may overcome"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And to know how to rule in His kingdom as kings,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "That His kingship thru us be expressed o’er all things."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "2"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Today we must learn to submit to His throne,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "How to have a strict life and His government own;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "His authority then we’ll be able to share,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "O’er the nations to rule with God’s Son as the heir."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "3"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "With a life strict to self we must righteousness hold,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Kind to others in peace, and with God joyful, bold;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "In the Kingdom’s reality e’er to remain,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "For its manifestation prepared thus to reign."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "4"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Then Christ when He comes with the kingdom from God"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Will to us grant His kingship to share as reward;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Thus the Lord will His righteousness thru us maintain"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And His wisdom to heavenly powers make plain."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "5"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "For this the Apostle pressed on at all cost,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "For the Kingdom assured that he would not be lost;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "’Tis for this he charged others, Be true to the Lord."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "That the Kingdom might be unto them a reward."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "6"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "O Lord, give us grace for Thy Kingdom to live,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "To be trained that Thou may the reward to us give;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Make the Kingdom’s reality our exercise,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "That its manifestation may be our great prize."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "7"
    }
